project-challenges: It's tested, works well with other gems, and has been downloaded over 200 times.
project-inspiration: It's difficult to get data about the Bay Area real estate market. The data is locked up across many different providers, and there is no single API for any of this data.
project-lessons-learned: Working with the San Franscisco County records system is a pain. Ideally, I'd like to integrate more advanced reporting features, like getting aggregate data for a block.
project-accomplishments: It's tested, works well with other gems, and has been downloaded over 200 times.
project-subtitle: Lightweight gem to discover information about San Francisco real estate.
